name: Flying Air Canada Express' Dash 8-400 to NORTHERN ONTARIO!
description:
Back in January of this year, I needed to get to Timmins for a very specific reason - to fly on the very last Classic Dash 8 flight with Air Canada Express, from there back to Toronto.

Obviously though, I had to get to Timmins first, and flew in the back of this Air Canada Express Dash 8-400 for a frigid winter flight up to Northern Ontario!
